ValueBasedHhsHccRiskAdjOutcomesDataMart

The value-based HHS-HCC outcomes data mart includes patient level outcomes for value-based measures. Each row represents outcomes for a patient calculated for a specific value-based program, performance period, calculation period, measure, summarization date, coverage event, and product line. For roll-up programs, constituent performance period is also included.

Properties

Reporting table name
dbo.ValueBasedHhsHccRiskAdjOutcomesDataMart
Granularity
A patient outcome for a program, performance period, calculation period, measure, summary date, coverage event, and product line. For roll-up programs, constituent performance period is also included.
